@startuml
title Dashboard / Journey Computation — Activity

start
:Load patients & journeys;
:For each patient: select
latest ACTIVE PatientJourney;
:Apply JourneyTemplate entries
(offsets/windows from startDate);
:Apply modifications
(ADD_STEP, REMOVE_STEP,
SWITCH_TEMPLATE);
:Overlay research module
entries if researchModuleIds
are present;
:Hydrate instructions
(resolve instructionTemplateId
→ content, or use
instructionText fallback);
:Compute effective steps
(getEffectiveSteps);
:Map effective steps to
queue/category;
:Build dashboard Case rows
with computed category
and nextStep;
stop

@enduml
